      "updated": 1773767281256,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Entry / Interface Layer  |  Partial\nPython SDK exists only as a public shape today. Future CLI is planned. Caller owns when runs are triggered.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 43,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Entry / Interface Layer  |  Partial\nPython SDK exists only as a public shape today. Future CLI is planned. Caller owns when runs are triggered.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aF",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "workflow-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 460,
      "y": 350,
      "width": 1002,
      "height": 72,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "seed": 1017,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1399713297,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773767281256,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Workflow Layer  |  Partial\nOwns lifecycle orchestration and public result contract.\nTransition helper and result envelope are done. Full prepare / check / analyze / close / promote execution is not done yet.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 67,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Workflow Layer  |  Partial\nOwns lifecycle orchestration and public result contract.\nTransition helper and result envelope are done. Full prepare / check / analyze / close / promote execution is not done yet.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aG",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
